comments: Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Dinwiddie's (DAL) path and marginal contact occurs as the two players come together during the pick.
Powell (DAL) avoids making contact with Ayton's (PHX) arm and legally contests the turnaround shot attempt.
Craig (PHX) and Bullock (DAL) mutually engage during the rebounding opportunity and incidental foot to foot contact occurs and Bullock briefly loses his balance.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) faces Johnson (PHX) as the two players mutually engage during the rebound and marginal contact occurs prior to Johnson securing the loose ball.
Finney-Smith (DAL) legally contests Bridges' (PHX) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Bullock (DAL) clamps and holds Craig's (PHX) left arm, which affects Craig's range of motion during the rebounding opportunity.
Bridges (PHX) places and immediately removes his hand from Powell's (DAL) side and the contact away from the ball is marginal.
Powell (DAL) firms up on his left leg and marginal contact occurs as Craig (PHX) fights over the pick.
Bullock (DAL) maintains legal positioning inside the court of play and does not step out of bounds while in possession of the ball.
Bridges (PHX) brings his arm around Dinwiddie (DAL) and marginal contact occurs that Dinwiddie is able to play on through.
Craig (PHX) goes into the air and rotates his body, delivering contact to Dinwiddie (DAL) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Powell (DAL) and Johnson (PHX) mutually engage and disengage during the loose ball and the contact is marginal.
Bridges (PHX) steps inside the three-point arc before Dinwiddie releases his free throw attempt.
Dinwiddie (DAL) briefly brings his off-arm back and marginal arm contact occurs with Johnson (PHX) during the drive.
Bullock (DAL) establishes himself in Bridges' (PHX) path and does not deliver contact during the pick.
Johnson (PHX) makes direct contact with the ball and dislodges it from Dinwiddie (DAL) after his gather into the driving shot attempt.
The shot clock expires during Dallas' possession. The ball is properly awarded to Phoenix.
Ayton (PHX) firms up on his right leg and marginal contact occurs as Bullock (DAL) fights around the pick.
Powell (DAL) legally contests Paul's (PHX) driving shot attempt.
Paul (PHX) brings his hands towards the ball and marginal contact occurs with Finney-Smith (DAL) during his dribble in the frontcourt.
Ayton (PHX) and Craig (PHX) get their hands to the ball and dislodge it from Powell's (DAL) grasp during the layup attempt at the basket. The arm contact after the dislodge is considered incidental.

Replay review of the out of bounds called on Craig (PHX) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Craig (PHX) and Ayton (PHX) cleanly dislodge the ball from Powell (DAL), who avoids making contact with it after the dislodge. Possession is retained by Dallas.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) establishes himself in Ayton's (PHX) path and marginal contact occurs as the two players come together during the screen.
Dinwiddie (DAL) and Craig (PHX) engage and disengage as the screen is set and the contact is marginal.
Finney-Smith (DAL) establishes himself in Craig's (PHX) path and marginal contact occurs as the two players come together during the pick.
Ayton (PHX) legally contests Finney-Smith's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) lightly brushes Finney-Smith's (DAL) sides and the contact away from the ball is marginal.
Green (DAL) legally contests Paul's (PHX) driving shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (DAL) and Johnson (PHX) engage and disengage during the inbound and the contact is marginal.
Craig (PHX) lightly brushes Finney-Smith's (DAL) front as he releases the pass and the contact is marginal.
Paul (PHX) commits a take foul on Bullock (DAL).
Ayton (PHX) initiates contact with Powell (DAL) that dislodges the offensive player as he is attempting to secure the loose ball.
Finney-Smith (DAL) and Bridges (PHX) engage and disengage after the screen is set and the contact is marginal.
Johnson (PHX) firms up on his right leg and marginal contact occurs as Hardaway Jr. (DAL) fights over the screen.
Dinwiddie (DAL) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt. Paul releases the shot and goes to the ground on his own accord.
